<p>John and Dave have a great show this week, answering questions about setting Mail&rsquo;s default sending account, enabling Photo Stream without a computer in the mix, understanding why OS X manages your Address Book the way it does, diagnosing both sleep issues AND runaway process issues, and much, much more. Plus, there&rsquo;s another timely summer, lightning-related discussion thrown in, as well. Don&rsquo;t miss this one, folks! Download and enjoy today.</p>
